item.title: CVE-2019-1003007|2024-09-17T03:08:27.801Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20warnings%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery vulnerability exists in Jenkins Warnings Plugin 5.0.0 and earlier in src/main/java/hudson/plugins/warnings/GroovyParser.java that allows attackers to execute arbitrary code via a form validation HTTP endpoint.
